  <description><![CDATA[<p>See Italy by rail on our Absolute Italy 10-night self-guided tour. With high speed connections to the major cities, getting around by train couldn’t be easier. Sit back and enjoy the journey, hopping between <a data-udi="umb://document/57bc5f34b7074843b7f19f3fc6cb7ac4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/57bc5f34b7074843b7f19f3fc6cb7ac4}" title="Rome">Rome</a>, Florence, La Spezia, Milan and Venice, passing through the Italian countryside. We’ve planned an itinerary with train tickets and things like excursions to the Colosseum, Naples and Pompeii, Tuscany and wine tasting, the Cinque Terre villages and Lake Como all included – so all you need to do is soak up the sights and atmosphere of this beautiful country.</p>
<div>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/amalfi-coast-walkingt#Tour highlights">Tour highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/amalfi-coast-walking#Itinerary&quot;">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/amalfi-coast-walking#Your holiday includes">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/amalfi-coast-walking#Hotels">Hotels</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/amalfi-coast-walking#Departure dates">Departure dates</a></h2>
